<h2>Create a New Message</h2>

<p>Have something to share with the community? Use the form below to post your thoughts, announcements, questions, or even start a fun discussion.</p>

<section class="message-info">
  <h3>💬 What Can You Post?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>📢 Announcements</li>
    <li>❓ Questions or polls</li>
    <li>😄 Funny or interesting experiences</li>
    <li>💡 Tips, tutorials, or insights</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<form action="/new-message" method="POST" class="form-message">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="title">Title:</label>
    <input
      type="text"
      name="title"
      id="title"
      placeholder="Enter a clear, eye-catching title"
      required
    />
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="content">Message Content:</label>
    <textarea
      name="content"
      id="content"
      rows="6"
      placeholder="Write your message here..."
      required
    ></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <p><strong>Reminder:</strong> Be respectful and kind. Messages are public and reflect the tone of our community.</p>
  </div>

  <button type="submit">📨 Post Your Message</button>
</form>

<section class="posting-tips">
  <h4>🛠 Tips for Better Engagement</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Use formatting and spacing to improve readability</li>
    <li>Be specific and descriptive in your title</li>
    <li>Use emojis sparingly to add personality</li>
    <li>Respond to others once your message is posted</li>
  </ul>
</section>
